                <p style="text-align: left; ">This research is part of the SNSF-funded research project The TeraPixel Panorama Project, led by co-author Prof. Sarah Kenderdine and Dr. Daniel Jaquet (Grant number 224000).</p>
                <p style="text-align: left; ">We would like to extend our special thanks to George Bruseker and Takin.solutions Ltd. for their insightful comments and advice regarding the utilization of CRMaaa.</p>
            </div>
