                <head>Online Resources</head>
                <p style="text-align: left; ">RDF data for the knowledge graph presented in this paper: 
                    <ref target="https://purl.archive.org/chauraph/dh2025/rdf">https://purl.archive.org/chauraph/dh2025/rdf</ref>
                </p>
            </div>
